`hotkeys for xmonad`

mod == alt
==========


****
mod+number(1-9) - switch to ~N desktop
mod+shift+number(1-9) - move the window to the ~N desktop
mod+shift+enter - new terminal
mod+p - dmenu
mod+shift+c - close the current window
mod+ctrl - switch language
mod+j or mod+tab - swap the current window and the next
mod+k - swap the current window and the previous one
mod+lmb(left mouse button) - moving the window with the mouse
mod+rmb(right mouse button) - resizing the window with the mouse
mod+space - change window position
mod+q - reboot xmonad
mod+F7 - -2 volume
mod+F8 - +2 volume
****


## recompile and restart
xmonad --recompile && xmonad --restart
